.go`](internal/worker/outbox.go)","","## D) ACK pipeline phase 3 (`delivery_ack`, `read_ack`)","","Design need:","","- Tach 3 muc ack: `server_ack`, `delivery_ack`, `read_ack`.","","Implemented by:","","- WS receives `ack_delivery` / `ack_read`.","- Core writes into `message_receipts` idempotently.","- `read_ack` update read pointer theo monotonic rule.","- Core emits outbox events cho ack updates.","","Code:","","- [`internal/transport/ws.go`](internal/transport/ws.go)","- [`internal/core/service.go`](internal/core/service.go) (`RecordDeliveryAck`, `RecordReadAck`)","- [`internal/db/schema.go`](internal/db/schema.go) (`message_receipts`)","","## E) Monotonic read state (no read-pointer regression)","","Design need:","","- Neu out-of-order read ack den, read pointer khong duoc lui.","","Implemented by:","","- Compare `targetSeq` vs current seq.","- Chi update `members.last_read_message_id` khi `targetSeq > currentSeq`.","","Code:","","- [`internal/core/service.go`](internal/core/service.go) (`shouldAdvanceReadPointer`, `RecordReadAck`)","- Test: [`internal/core/service_test.go`](internal/core/service_test.go)","","---","","## 3) Request flows with diagrams","","## Send message flow","","```mermaid","sequenceDiagram","    participant Client","    participant Gateway","    participant Core","    participant Postgres","    participant Worker","    participant Redis","","    Client->>Gateway: send_message","    Gateway->>Core: CreateMessage(input)","    Core->>Postgres: tx(insert messages + outbox_events)","    Core-->>Gateway: Message + duplicated flag","    Gateway-->>Client: server_ack","    Worker->>Postgres: poll pending outbox","    Worker->>Redis: XADD chat.conv.{conversation_id}","    Worker->>Postgres: mark published","```","","Main code:","","- [`internal/transport/ws.go`](internal/transport/ws.go)","- [`internal/core/service.go`](internal/core/service.go)","- [`internal/worker/outbox.go`](internal/worker/outbox.go)","","## Delivery/read ack flow","","```merma